![Python 3.10+](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.10%2B-blue) ![License: CC BY 4.0](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-CC%20BY%204.0-lightgrey) ![Last updated: Mar 2026](https://img.shields.io/badge/last%20updated-Mar%202026-green)

Reproducible fine-tuning recipe for Whisper-Large on Icelandic conversational speech.
Includes a segment-aware dataset builder for the Spjallrómur corpus and a full training
script with early stopping, WER evaluation, and held-out test scoring.

> **Results:** Fine-tuning on Spjallrómur reduces WER from 46.2% → 28.6% compared to read-speech adaptation alone — a 38% relative improvement.

---

