## Data access

The Spjallrómur conversational corpus is **not redistributed here**. Obtain it directly from CLARIN-IS:

> https://repository.clarin.is/repository/xmlui/handle/20.500.12537/187

After extraction, the corpus must follow this folder structure:

```
<DATA_DIR>/
  <conversation_id>/
    speaker_a_convo*.wav
    speaker_b_convo*.wav
    speaker_a_convo*_transcript.json
    speaker_b_convo*_transcript.json
```

Each transcript JSON must contain segment-level timestamps with word-level transcription entries.

